description: Lundin Energy AB is an independent oil and gas exploration and production company. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 456 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2001-09-06. The Company’s main business is the exploration, the development of, and the production of oil and gas. The firm maintains a portfolio of oil and gas production assets and development projects in various countries with exposure to exploration opportunities. The Group operates within several geographical areas with a focus on Norway.
naicsNationalIndustry: Crude Petroleum and Natural Gas Extraction
